BOJ Governor Shirakawa Says Japan Banking System Healthy

-- B y   T o r u   F u j i o k a
-- 
2011-09-29T07:00:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/boj-governor-shirakawa-says-japan-banking-system-healthy.html
Bank of Japan (8301)  Governor Masaaki
Shirakawa said the nation’s banking system is healthy.  He also said in a speech in  Tokyo  today that the yen is
strengthening because it’s considered a relatively safe
currency.  To contact the reporter on this story:
